                <h1>Dune</h1>
                <h2>Genre: Science Fiction</h2>
                <p>Description: Set on the desert planet Arrakis, Dune is the story of the boy Paul Atreides, heir to a
                    noble family tasked with ruling an inhospitable world where the only thing of value is the "spice"
                    melange, a drug capable of extending life and enhancing consciousness. Coveted across the known
                    universe, melange is a prize worth killing for. When House Atreides is betrayed, the destruction of
                    Paul's family will set the boy on a journey toward a destiny greater than he ever could have
                    imagined, and one that will change the course of history forever.</p>
