                <h1>The Hobbit</h1>
                <h2>Genre: Fantasy</h2>
                <p>Description: Bilbo Baggins is a hobbit who enjoys a comfortable, unambitious life, rarely traveling
                    further than the pantry of his hobbit-hole. But his contentment is disturbed when the wizard Gandalf
                    and a company of thirteen dwarves arrive on his doorstep one day to whisk him away on an adventure.
                    They have launched a plot to raid the treasure hoard guarded by the dragon Smaug, and Bilbo
                    reluctantly joins their quest, sharpening his wits and skills along a journey that takes him from
                    his snug, beloved hobbit-hole to the Lonely Mountain.</p>
